---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="How We Taste | Enoversa">
    <Navigation />

    <main id="main-content" class="pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-24 border-b border-line pb-12">
            <span
                class="font-mono text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block"
                >The Tasting Index</span
            >
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-tighter mb-8">
                How We <span class="italic font-serif text-text-dim">Taste.</span>
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl font-light text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"
            >
                We score five aspects of every wine from 0 to 2.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-24">
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        01. Energy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        MOVEMENT & FRESHNESS
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Does the wine feel alive in the glass? We look at
                        acidity, movement, freshness, and how it changes after
                        opening.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">0 - Flat</span
                            >Heavy, tired, or static.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Steady</span
                            >Enough movement to hold our attention.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Charged</span
                            >Energetic from the first glass to the last.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        02. Drinkability
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        THE NEXT SIP
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Do we want to take another sip? Texture, alcohol,
                        extraction, and faults can all affect how easily the
                        wine moves.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Tiring</span
                            >Difficult to finish.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Drinkable</span
                            >Enjoyable, with some reservations.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Compelling</span
                            >The glass empties quickly.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        03. Balance
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        PROPORTION
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Does any element dominate the wine? We consider
                        acidity, tannin, alcohol, fruit, oak, and texture.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Disjointed</span
                            >One or more elements get in the way.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Mostly together</span
                            >Balanced, though the seams are visible.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Integrated</span
                            >Nothing feels out of place.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        04. Complexity
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        CHANGE OVER TIME
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Does the wine change in the glass? We look for new
                        aromas, textures, and flavours as it opens.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Simple</span
                            >One clear idea, with little development.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Layered</span
                            >More appears with time.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Evolving</span
                            >It continues to change throughout the bottle.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        05. Emotion
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">WHAT REMAINS</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Did the wine leave an impression beyond its technical
                        qualities?
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Forgettable</span
                            >Little remains after the glass.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Distinctive</span
                            >Something about it stays with us.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Memorable</span
                            >We are still thinking about it weeks later.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <aside class="border-y border-line py-10 md:ml-[33.333%]">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent uppercase tracking-widest">
                    About the total
                </span>
                <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
                    The total is a summary, not a ranking. Two wines with the
                    same score may offer completely different experiences.
                </p>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>
